Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰拜托你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麽目的調查數數歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很多調查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數數歌說到的嫦娥狼傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始只是以為那是動物信仰的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是調查之中  卻萌發了一個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果嫦娥狼和普通的狼是完全不同的種類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如有著人類的外型和內心的人狼什麽的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫦娥狼的真面目  那是是人非人的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  如你所說我們就是嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身負被詛咒宿命的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝霧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你帶路  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要放我走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麽多  今天的事就忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也別再牽扯進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次估計救不了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的存在  非常礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做錯了什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎麽樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自放走可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是喜歡超自然現象的神墮人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為無視掉沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就這樣放任接近秘密的人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣就對神墮人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不正是違背了戒律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來那個女孩是獵戶大人的同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前摘花五十鈴差點墮落的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為獵戶大人稍有些公私不分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想有無謂的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于落神之式能請交給擔任獵戶的我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  請恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今後請勿獨斷行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這樣的問題只不過是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天我委托了「專家」  去把強勁的「蜜」排除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田家的當家  重三大人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們親手抓住「蜜」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓「專家」來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不直接下手的話也不算違背戒律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來交給「專家」的名單上也有獵戶大人的同學的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花五十鈴也缺席嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝霧要也難得請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在打算去地方資料館調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要管好自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽問題的話要馬上去「中心」…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的身體只有自己最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麽事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵餵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西大人  怎麽辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起騷動就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視這個小鬼  直接去「蜜」那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做的兔耳青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡兔耳青蛙先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的話送給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人的病症的真正治療法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其實現就是你的理想對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了  在猶豫什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以相信你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說是神人的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格來說不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人和人類是不同的種類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的種類  不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說  是人非人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本和普通人類沒有區別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去那個被詛咒的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在有些場合下會抑制不住衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了扭轉這可悲的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此希望能和你的公司一同開發疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須…一定要完成這個研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此請你助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  雖然我不該這麽說  但能否請你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份資料上記載的神人的事情只有你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽…為什麽跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裏  趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你跟我們來一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同學  為什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當家的命令  請讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經忠告過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再違背當家的命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的地位真的會岌岌可危
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣值得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就先退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  院長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了  這種時候來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…今天是作為栉名田家的人來此的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼大人終于要去神域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那小姐  不  白狼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有心理准備了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事俱備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥…  難不成！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些家夥  又要從我這裏掠奪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶大人  請問您這是何意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天您幫助朝霧要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這回您又妨礙我們捉拿九澄博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此  遵照獵戶的守則
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將追究您應負的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠  葛西所言當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除你獵戶的身份  並禁止你出門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏不舒服了麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯…  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  明天我們一起去探望香織姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西  是什麽…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今天  一位很可愛的大姐姐給的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像穿的是跟哥哥一樣的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發生過什麽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家夥是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵  是的  我是九澄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽晚了還麻煩你  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織姐  去哪兒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是搬家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一聲不吭的  說走就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠大哥也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能先回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也可以  可為什麽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個地方想去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到  你竟會主動聯系我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你想說的  又是什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後  我又想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我周圍  有被賢木先生你稱為怪物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  我很怕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  我也有過被他們襲擊過的經曆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得  應該是事出有因的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  應該是有非這麽做不可的理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  那個手執巨鐮的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同班同學栉名田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在這之前  曾經救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你一命？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幾乎可以說是一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想搞個明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些家夥裏面  有良心的人  也許還是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那樣  要是我有證據的話呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我有他們是極度危險的怪物的證據呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回我就讓你好好看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  還是那個強效的蜜的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們委托的「專家」來電話說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經成功地將那「蜜」——九澄博士給抓到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監禁地點仍舊是以前的那處工地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是優秀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  處置的事  就交給那「專家」來幹對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  聽他說  之後就按照家主大人的意思  隨時執行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麽  那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田眠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實交代  九澄君在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費我好大功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我不會馬上殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想死得這麽容易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于你  對于殺了三重子的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會給予和我悲痛相當的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是九澄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  賢木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  現在就出來麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你不是想知道麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你要給我看什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢木先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢木先生  開門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:21:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄…  君…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜大眼睛好好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你想知道的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九吻所為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難逆心之火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未嘗禁果味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因抑心魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:23:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑法可乎悲？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其人當為我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來  我究竟都在看著什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟都在相信著什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.48,0:24:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若還不能憑著自己的一雙手臂  以及一雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將真相看個一清二楚的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  密室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:02.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:08.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接連著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:21.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口難開 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:27.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}漸次斑駁  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:34.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至終焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:40.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之間  逢見君影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:56.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故鄉迢迢  時之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無愛無心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:14.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻蒼空
